{"tid":2435025,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國將用於疫情應對的中國商品關稅豁免期延長六個月","createTime":"2021-03-06T02:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T03:13:27.000Z","uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3bfbf9e23a816510665437581337ed0007f28cc3","tid":2435025,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:40:36.000Z","msg":"【彭博】-- 美國將把針對中國產口罩、清潔用品及其它個人防護設備的關稅豁免期延長六個月，以免抗擊新冠疫情之際相關成本上升。<br />\n<br />\n根據彭博新聞社看到的美國貿易代表通知草案，這會影響99種產品。豁免期已於去年12月延長過一次，這次將持續到9月末。<br />\n<br />\n川普政府依據1974年貿易法案第301條對中國產品加徵關稅，理由是中國竊取智慧財產權和強迫美國公司轉讓技術。一年前在新冠疫情爆發時，美國對肥皂、口罩、醫療物資和實驗室設備等豁免了關稅。<br />\n<br />\n拜登政府尚未表示是否會維持川普關稅，但白宮受到了來自商業界和議員要求將抗疫相關產品豁免關稅的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n原文標題U.S. Extends Tariff Exclusion on China Virus Supplies 6 Months<br />\nFor more articles like this, please visit us at <a href=\"http://bloomberg.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbloomberg.com&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n%2FxvqPrKL%2FWP0%2BN3ppmbOOw%3D&h=4ff3489c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a><br />\nSubscribe now to stay ahead with the most trusted business news source.<br />\n&copy;2021 Bloomberg L.P."},{"pid":"cf0991b12e8fbf420a1eaf2c6569f648f7316773","tid":2435025,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:43:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uy6FPQG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUy6FPQG.gif&h=9829becd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a6fea37e93c9772b024d8ad62ea3b653ea49dc4","tid":2435025,"uid":220431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf0991b12e8fbf420a1eaf2c6569f648f7316773","tid":2435025,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:43:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uy6FPQG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUy6FPQG.gif&h=9829becd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b9877c7a0458cf83917ccd6afedaef953b12ec","tid":2435025,"uid":377064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T03:09:01.000Z","msg":"聽講之前有單新聞話美國有好多呢啲醫療用品都係中國造"},{"pid":"ffdf43e63e70c29435496a45e32572de95cb4689","tid":2435025,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95b9877c7a0458cf83917ccd6afedaef953b12ec","tid":2435025,"uid":377064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T03:09:01.000Z","msg":"聽講之前有單新聞話美國有好多呢啲醫療用品都係中國造"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T03:13:27.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係啦<br />\n所以香港口罩生意應該不會死<br />\n仲有得做"}]}